      "created_at": "2019-05-10T15:51:20.714Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Ka nje ministri mjedisi qe duhet ti studioje pasojat perpara se te ndertohet hec jo pasi eshte bere fakt I kryer.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
